title: Somewhat retired D5 player looking for a team to get back in league ( Support main)
body: BIO: Im a D5 player (S5), my account was recently terminated, not banned, terminated. Why you ask? because it was hacked, fraudulent credit cards were used on my account so now I'm a level 29 trying to keep my skill in tact while playing up to level 30 and hopefully getting into diamond or a LCS team. I main support and sometimes Adc and thats about it.
